{"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/Workflow\/documentation\/Workflow\/RenderContext"},"metadata":{"externalID":"s:8Workflow13RenderContextC","role":"symbol","symbolKind":"class","roleHeading":"Class","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"RenderContext","kind":"identifier"}],"modules":[{"name":"Workflow"}],"title":"RenderContext","fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"RenderContext","kind":"identifier"}]},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"RenderContext","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"<","kind":"text"},{"text":"WorkflowType","kind":"genericParameter"},{"text":"> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"where","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"WorkflowType","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" : ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Workflow","preciseIdentifier":"s:8WorkflowAAP","kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/Workflow\/documentation\/Workflow\/Workflow"}],"platforms":["iOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"anchor":"overview","level":2,"text":"Overview","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"During a render pass, a workflow may want to defer to a child","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"workflow to render some portion of its content. For example,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"a workflow that renders to a split-screen view model might","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"delegate to child A for the left side, and child B for the right","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"side view models. Nesting allows for a fractal tree that is constructed","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"out of many small parts.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"If a parent wants to delegate to a child workflow, it must first","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"create an instance of that workflow. This can be thought of as the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"model of the child workflow. It does not contain any active state,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"it simply contains the data necessary to create or update a workflow","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"node.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The parent then calls ","type":"text"},{"code":"render(workflow:outputMap:)","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"with two values:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The child workflow.","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"A closure that transforms the child’s output events into the parent’s","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Event"},{"text":" type so that the parent can respond to events generated by","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the child.","type":"text"}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If the parent had previously rendered a child of the same type, the existing"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"child workflow node is updated."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If the parent had not rendered a child of the same type in the previous"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"render pass, a new child workflow node is generated."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The infrastructure then performs a render pass on the child to obtain its"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Rendering"},{"type":"text","text":" value, which is then returned to the caller."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"sections":[],"abstract":[{"code":"RenderContext","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" is the composition point for the workflow tree.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/workflow\/rendercontext"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/Workflow\/documentation\/Workflow"]]},"topicSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/Workflow\/documentation\/Workflow\/RenderContext\/makeOutputSink()","doc:\/\/Workflow\/documentation\/Workflow\/RenderContext\/makeSink(of:)","doc:\/\/Workflow\/documentation\/Workflow\/RenderContext\/makeSink(of:onEvent:)","doc:\/\/Workflow\/documentation\/Workflow\/RenderContext\/makeStateMutationSink()","doc:\/\/Workflow\/documentation\/Workflow\/RenderContext\/runSideEffect(key:action:)"],"generated":true,"title":"Instance Methods","anchor":"Instance-Methods"}],"references":{"doc://Workflow/documentation/Workflow/RenderContext/makeStateMutationSink()":{"type":"topic","title":"makeStateMutationSink()","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"makeStateMutationSink"},{"kind":"text","text":"() -> "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:8Workflow17StateMutationSinkV","text":"StateMutationSink"},{"kind":"text","text":"<"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:8Workflow13RenderContextC0A4Typexmfp","text":"WorkflowType"},{"kind":"text","text":">"}],"conformance":{"conformancePrefix":[{"type":"text","text":"Conforms when"}],"availabilityPrefix":[{"type":"text","text":"Available when"}],"constraints":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"WorkflowType"},{"type":"text","text":" conforms to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Workflow"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},"url":"\/documentation\/workflow\/rendercontext\/makestatemutationsink()","identifier":"doc:\/\/Workflow\/documentation\/Workflow\/RenderContext\/makeStateMutationSink()","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"Creates ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"StateMutationSink"},{"text":".","type":"text"}]},"doc://Workflow/documentation/Workflow/RenderContext/ma